````markdown
# 🌐 HTML Roadmap: Beginner to Advanced

Master HTML – the foundation of the web. This roadmap takes you from writing your first tags to building responsive, accessible, and SEO-optimized websites.

---

## 📘 Table of Contents

- [Introduction to HTML](#introduction-to-html)
- [Basic HTML Elements](#basic-html-elements)
- [Intermediate HTML Concepts](#intermediate-html-concepts)
- [Advanced HTML Features](#advanced-html-features)
- [SEO, Accessibility & Best Practices](#seo-accessibility--best-practices)
- [HTML Project Ideas](#html-project-ideas)
- [Resources](#resources)

---

## 🟢 Introduction to HTML

- What is HTML?
- How the web works (HTML + CSS + JS)
- HTML document structure (`<!DOCTYPE html>`, `<html>`, `<head>`, `<body>`)
- Setting up an HTML file

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>My First Page</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hello World</h1>
  </body>
</html>
```
````

---

## 🧱 Basic HTML Elements

### Text Elements

- `<h1>` to `<h6>` – Headings
- `<p>` – Paragraph
- `<br>`, `<hr>`
- `<strong>`, `<em>`, `<mark>`, `<small>`

### Lists

- `<ul>`, `<ol>`, `<li>`
- `<dl>`, `<dt>`, `<dd>`

### Links & Media

- `<a href="">`
- `<img src="" alt="">`
- `<video>`, `<audio>`, `<iframe>`

### Forms

- `<form>`, `<input>`, `<textarea>`, `<button>`
- `<select>`, `<option>`, `<label>`, `name`, `value`, `placeholder`, `required`

### Tables

- `<table>`, `<tr>`, `<td>`, `<th>`, `<thead>`, `<tbody>`

---

## 🟡 Intermediate HTML Concepts

### Semantic HTML

- `<header>`, `<footer>`, `<nav>`, `<section>`, `<article>`, `<aside>`, `<main>`

### Form Enhancements

- `type="email"`, `type="number"`, `type="date"`
- Form validation attributes: `required`, `pattern`, `min`, `max`, `readonly`

### Meta Tags

- `<meta charset="UTF-8">`
- `<meta name="viewport">`
- `<meta name="description">`

### Favicons

- `<link rel="icon" href="favicon.ico">`

### HTML Entities

- `&copy;`, `&amp;`, `&lt;`, `&gt;`, `&nbsp;`

---

## 🔵 Advanced HTML Features

### Embedded Content

- `<iframe>` for videos/maps
- `<embed>` and `<object>`

### Data Attributes

```html
<button data-user-id="42">Click Me</button>
```

### SVG & Canvas

- `<svg>`, `<circle>`, `<path>`
- `<canvas>` for drawing with JS

### Web Storage

- `localStorage`, `sessionStorage` via JS

### Custom Elements (Web Components)

- `<my-component></my-component>`

---

## 🧠 SEO, Accessibility & Best Practices

### SEO (Search Engine Optimization)

- Use semantic tags properly
- Proper heading hierarchy
- Meta descriptions
- Alt text for images

### Accessibility (a11y)

- `alt`, `aria-label`, `aria-hidden`
- Keyboard navigation support
- Use landmarks: `<main>`, `<nav>`, `<footer>`

### Best Practices

- Keep HTML structure clean and nested
- Use comments: `<!-- This is a comment -->`
- Don’t skip heading levels
- Avoid inline styles

---

## 💡 HTML Project Ideas

| Project              | Concepts Used                           |
| -------------------- | --------------------------------------- |
| Personal Portfolio   | Semantic HTML, Forms, Links, Images     |
| Resume Webpage       | Lists, Tables, Typography               |
| Product Landing Page | Forms, Multimedia, Responsiveness       |
| Blog Layout          | Articles, Sections, Metadata            |
| Survey Form          | Input fields, Validation, Accessibility |

